OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779962735
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FA mother who was the victim of
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse says the justice system
OL,8,Fhas allowed the manipulation she's
OL,9,Ffaced to continue.
OL,11,FShe is among a dozen women ITV News
OL,12,Fhas spoken to who say family
OL,13,Fcourtrooms, where custody rights of
OL,14,Fchildren are decided, are being used
OL,15,Fas weapons for abusers.
OL,17,FKate says her legal ordeal not only
OL,18,Fcost years of her life but also over a
OL,19,F#100,000, which resulted in her mother
OL,20,Fhaving to sell her home.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
