PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779962735
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FThe stress and torment continued
OL,7,Fdespite leaving the abusive
OL,8,Frelationship.
OL,10,F"He just wouldn't leave outside my
OL,11,Fhouse and - for hours and hours. Your
OL,12,Fhome becomes a prison.
OL,14,F"It's taken four years of my life and
OL,15,Fmy child's life - and we've now sat at
OL,16,Fcourt six times in total. Personally,
OL,17,FI would never go back to family court
OL,18,Fagain. It doesn't work.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779962735
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,F"I'm under the threat of my
OL,7,Fabuser...with what the family courts
OL,8,Fhave done. And they have kept him
OL,9,Ffirmly in our life, but I will never
OL,10,Ftrust family court ever again."
OL,12,FAnother mother says she felt dismissed
OL,13,Fby judges even though her former
OL,14,Fpartner had been sent to prison.
OL,16,FSpeaking anonymously, Sophie says her
OL,17,Fchildren were forced into unsafe
OL,18,Fcontact with their father.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779962735
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,F"Before the family court the last
OL,7,Fthing he said to me was that he wanted
OL,8,Fto kill me.
OL,10,F"I think I just assumed that I was
OL,11,Fgoing to be able to explain the full
OL,12,Fhistory and I would get the same jaw
OL,13,Fdrop response I'd had from other
OL,14,Fpeople and professionals - and they
OL,15,Fwere gonna go 'wow this guy's
OL,16,Fdangerous, we need to keep these
OL,17,Fchildren safe'...and most of it isn't
OL,18,Fheard, most of it is disregarded."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779962735
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,F"I've got friends that I'm aware that
OL,7,Fwon't leave their abusive partners
OL,8,Fbecause the situation they're in, they
OL,9,Fknow they have a way to manage. And I
OL,10,Fthink they've seen how much of a
OL,11,Fbattle it's been for me."
OL,13,FJudges often order parents to use co-
OL,14,Fparenting apps, but these are used as
OL,15,Fanother form of control allowing
OL,16,Fabusive partners to send un-true
OL,17,Fallegations such as accusing mothers
OL,18,Fof 'poisoning their children'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
