OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779962735
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FCharities such as Stop Domestic Abuse
OL,7,Fsay they regularly hear from people
OL,8,Fworried about the process of going to
OL,9,Fcourt.
OL,11,FCEO Claire Lambon said the cycle of
OL,12,Fabuse can continue, "We see year on,
OL,13,Fevery year an increase in demand for
OL,14,Four services. And we have had many
OL,15,Fcases where the survivor in court has
OL,16,Freally had an anxious time because
OL,17,Fthey've come face to face with the
OL,18,Fabuser.
OL,20,F"The court case can be another weapon
OL,21,Fin perpetuating abuse."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779962735
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FFamily court barrister Dr Charlotte
OL,7,FProudman said, "Many think of the
OL,8,Ffamily court I think now as being a
OL,9,Fplayground for domestic abuse.
OL,11,F"And arguably things have got worse in
OL,12,Ffact over the last ten years I would
OL,13,Fsay and that's because of this notion
OL,14,Fof parental alienation which has
OL,15,Fstarted to gain huge amounts of
OL,16,Ftraction and power in family courts."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
