OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779962735
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice told us, "It
OL,7,Fis unacceptable for anyone to use the
OL,8,Ffamily courts to further distress
OL,9,Fvictims, which is why we are driving
OL,10,Fthrough reforms to give survivors
OL,11,Fearlier specialist support,
OL,12,Fstrengthening safeguards and shutting
OL,13,Fdown attempts to use the system as a
OL,14,Ftool of ongoing control.
OL,16,F"This includes requiring courts to
OL,17,Fconsider special measures - such as
OL,18,Fprotective screens or giving evidence
OL,19,Fby video link - to enable victims to
OL,20,Ffully participate in proceedings."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
